AOV x @nattesferd

Hi everybody! I'm @nattesferd - Stoked to be here on @artofvisuals today doing this takeover, please allow me to introduce myself, I'm a 25 year old Swede who became obsessed with photography 7 months ago. Long story short, this year I'm selling all of my belongings to pursue the life on the road doing what I love. I'm going to show you some photos of my favorite places I've been to so far, starting of with this shot taken at Kvalvika beach, Lofoten. (Stay tuned for more pictures throughout today by @nattesferd )
